00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:42,860
 When you see Jesus, there is always a response to follow

596
00:26:42,860 --> 00:26:46,020
 when you truly see Jesus.

597
00:26:46,020 --> 00:26:49,980
 But I think a lot of us haven't truly experienced Jesus.

598
00:26:49,980 --> 00:26:56,440
 Sure, we say I'm a Christian or yeah, I know about Jesus,

