00:27:56,420 --> 00:27:59,420
 Jesus lists out what it is not.

620
00:27:59,420 --> 00:28:03,100
 The will of God is not a relationship,

621
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:08,100
 or the will of God is not a resume of religious actions.

622
00:28:08,100 --> 00:28:10,940
 Let me say it one more time.

623
00:28:10,940 --> 00:28:14,100
 The will of God or a real relationship with Jesus

624
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:18,900
 is not a resume of religious actions.

625
00:28:18,900 --> 00:28:21,380
 Because when we hear, hey, do the will of my father,

626
00:28:21,380 --> 00:28:24,060
 that word do, it can be a red flag to some of us.

