00:30:15,720 --> 00:30:19,460
 He doesn't want your activity.

671
00:30:19,460 --> 00:30:20,740
 Again, he wants proximity.

672
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:21,860
 He wants you.

673
00:30:21,860 --> 00:30:25,940
 Now what you can do, he's telling these guys,

674
00:30:25,940 --> 00:30:28,680
 hey, the best of the best of the religious leaders,

