00:32:48,080 --> 00:32:49,860
 you can come before me and try to list up

730
00:32:49,860 --> 00:32:52,160
 all these impressive spiritual acts

731
00:32:52,160 --> 00:32:54,960
 on this religious resume and it doesn't matter.

732
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:59,300
 I'm not impressed by your deeds.

733
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:01,640
 I want you, I want you.

734
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:08,220
 Being a Christian is not just doing Christian things.

