00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:36,840
 He says this, "Who gets into heaven?

743
00:33:36,840 --> 00:33:38,660
 "Who spends eternity with me?

744
00:33:38,660 --> 00:33:41,900
 "The one who does the will of my father who is in heaven."

745
00:33:41,900 --> 00:33:45,920
 Knowing Jesus, knowing that you know,

746
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:50,720
 that you know, that you know is doing the will of God.

