00:34:39,040 --> 00:34:42,840
 Believing in his son, believing in his plan

765
00:34:42,840 --> 00:34:45,560
 for humanity, believing what we call the gospel,

766
00:34:45,560 --> 00:34:49,560
 the good news that Jesus, God's one and only son

