00:34:53,520 --> 00:34:56,680
 into our mess, into our broken world,

769
00:34:56,680 --> 00:34:59,720
 yet he remained perfect, making him the perfect sacrifice

770
00:34:59,720 --> 00:35:02,660
 because our sin deserved a penalty.

771
00:35:02,660 --> 00:35:07,880
 Our sin required a payment for a holy God.

772
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:10,280
 And Jesus was that perfect payment.

773
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:12,160
 He was sacrificed on the cross

774
00:35:12,160 --> 00:35:16,480
 and there the wrath of God poured out on him.

775
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,920
 And it should have been us.

776
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,840
 He died in our place.

